<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687648>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18–27. Pezothrips bactrianus. Paratype female, 18–24. (18) Head and pronotum; (19) Antenna; (20) Meso- and metanota; (21) Tergite II; (22) Tergite VII; (23) Tergites VIII–X; (24) Sternite VII (sculpture omitted). Male, 25–27. (25) Tergite IX; (26) Sternite VII; (27) Genitalia (hypomere & parameres), dorsal aspect, allotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3687648/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687654>
    dc:description "FIGURES 38–46. Pezothrips frontalis in SMF, female microptera, 38–43. (38) Head and pronotum; (39) Antenna; (40) Meso- and metanota; (41) Tergite II; (42) Tergites VII–X; (43) Sternite VII (sculpture omitted). (44) Metascutum, female macroptera, sculpture omitted. Male, 45–46. (45) Tergite IX; (46) Sternite VI (sculpture omitted)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3687654/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687658>
    dc:description "FIGURES 56–61. Pezothrips moravicus, holotype female. (56) Head and pronotum; (57) Antenna; (58) Mesonotum and metanota; (59) Tergite II; (60) Tergites VIII–X; (61) Sternite VII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3687658/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687660>
    dc:description "FIGURES 62–70. Pezothrips nadeshiko, n. sp., female, 62–77. (62) Head and pronotum; (63) Antenna; (64) Mesonotum and metascutum; (65) Tergite II; (66) Tergites VIII–X; (57) Sternite VII (sculpture omitted). Male, 68–70. (68) Tergite IX (sculpture omitted); (69) Sternite VII; (70) Genitalia (hypomere & parameres), left aspect." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3687660/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687662>
    dc:description "FIGURES 71–75. Pezothrips nigriventris, holotype female. (71) Head & pronotum; (72) Mesonotum and metasnota; (73) Tergite II; (74) Tergites VIII–X; (75) Sternite VII (sculpture omitted)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3687662/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687664>
    dc:description "FIGURES 76–81. Pezothrips pelikani, n. sp., lectotype female. (76) Head and pronotum; (77) Antenna; (78) Meso- and metanota; (79) Tergite II; (80) Tergites VII–X; (81) Sternite VII (sculpture omitted)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3687664/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687650>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28–31. Pezothrips cereus, paratype female. (28) Head and pronotum; (29) Mesonotum and metascutum; (30) Tergites VIII–X; (31) Sternite VII (sculpture omitted)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3687650/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687652>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32–37. Pezothrips dianthi. Female from Germany, 32–35. (32) Head and pronotum; (33) Antenna; (34) Mesonotum and metascutum; (35) Tergite II. Male from Germany, 36–37. (36) Tergite IX; (37) Sternite VII (sculpture omitted)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3687652/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3687656>
    dc:description "FIGURES 47–55. Pezothrips kellyanus. Female, 47–52. (47) Head and pronotum; (48) Antenna; (49) Mesonotum and metascutum; (50) Tergite II; (51) Tergites VIII–X; (52) Sternite VII (sculpture omitted). Male, 53–55. (53) Antenna; (54) Tergite IX (sculpture omitted); (55) Sternite VII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3687656/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

